Package: picar
Title: Pica Data Import and Extraction
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: "Donatus Herre <mail@herre.io> [aut, cre]"
Description: Import Pica data via Catmandu command line interface from different
    SRU interfaces and store content parsed as picaxml or ppxml to local json files.
    Afterwards you can read these files via jsonlite to extract specific pica tags.
License: file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    jsonlite
SystemRequirements: Perl, Catmandu::SRU, Catmandu::PICA
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
